Jean-Roger Caussimon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean-Roger_Caussimon 0 Jean-Roger Caussimon (24 July 1918 – 19 October 1985) was a French singer-songwriter and film actor. He appeared in 90 films between 1945 and 1985 but is better known for having worked with poet-singer Léo Ferré.
